The Downtown Miami Hilton is on the fringe of the downtown area but very close to the light rail and a short drive to S. Beach and Little Havana.	The staff upgraded us to larger room, with a terrific view of the downtown and port.	Room was clean, comfortable beds, with excellent view of the bay and downtown.	Our room was nicely decorated, great linens, flat screen tv and a beautiful view of Miami skyline.	Our room was very comfortable and had a amazing view of the city and of the bay.	The room was spacious and bathroom clean with great views over the bay and the breakfast was awesome, the staff throughout the hotel were very polite and helpful.